items.title: DOGE 'doesn't exist' with eight months left on its charter
items.description: U.S. President Donald Trump's Department of Government Efficiency has disbanded with eight months left to its mandate.

items.description: The row, the biggest China-Japan crisis in years, has spread to trade and cultural relations.

items.title: U.S. senators say Rubio told them Trump’s Ukraine peace plan is Russia’s ‘wish list.’ Rubio denies it
items.description: Lawmakers say Secretary of State Marco Rubio told them Trump's plan for peace in Ukraine is a "wish list" of the Russians.

items.title: Trump officials’ meeting with Russian in Miami spurs questions about latest Ukraine proposal
